      <Name>The Gates of the Temple</Name>
      <Description>Twenty foot glowing gates made of ancient oak and banded together with
steel towers before you.  A hooded monk stands before them with his head
bowed in quiet contemplation.  The small star-shaped keyhole appears to be
the only way to open the massive gates to the north.</Description>
